  // Open/claimable pool: a non-urgent task anyone can claim, with a manager confirming
  // the claim. While claimable it is "held" by its creator (assignedToId) but surfaced
  // in the Available Tasks pool, not as a normal assignment.
  claimable            Boolean      @default(false)
